# Force LF line endings on every detected text file, on every platform.
# Without this, Windows core.autocrlf rewrites CRLF→LF on commit, which
# desynchronises the manifest's per-pack sha256 (computed against working-
# tree bytes) from the bytes Git stores and GitHub raw serves.  text=auto
# lets Git decide what's text vs binary so images and other binaries
# aren't touched.
* text=auto eol=lf
